 nmcli d wifi hotspot ifname wlx1cbfce55cb92 ssid sean password password
 nmcli dev wifi show-password
 nmcli connection delete id Hotspot

-----
nmcli con add type wifi ifname wlx1cbfce55cb92 con-name Hotspot autoconnect yes ssid sean 
nmcli con modify Hotspot 802-11-wireless.mode ap 802-11-wireless.band bg ipv4.method shared
nmcli con modify Hotspot wifi-sec.key-mgmt wpa-psk
nmcli con modify Hotspot wifi-sec.psk password
nmcli con up Hotspot

to bring up after reboot:
UUID=$(grep uuid /etc/NetworkManager/system-connections/Hotspot | cut -d= -f2); nmcli con up uuid $UUID
=====
Or other

